&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or an informal discussion please contact our paediatric practice development team by e-mail on jas.khalsa@thh.nhs.uk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
